          output: 'We are the talk of the town. Everyone witnessed our followers
            mobilizing to save those in need throughout the city. By the time the
            waters recede, our temples lie in ruins, but our image is untarnished.

            [Gained
            30 Zeal, 10 Bliss & 70 Flock Lost 40 Wealth]

'
