          - rid: 107151359355650125
          - rid: 107151359355650126
          output: 'What a tragedy! Many of our heroic followers drown while attempting
            to save the innocent. Though our martyrs shall be remembered as heroes,
            the loss is undeniable. To worsen matters, our temples have been reduced
            to rubble.

            [Gained 50 Zeal & 25 Flock Lost 15 Bliss & 40
            Wealth]

'
